{
  "texts": [
    "This tool encompasses conversational interaction between GPT users.",
    "In a conversation, ChatGPT could react to human-sounding text input from the user.",
    "Its dialogue format allows it to respond to subsequent questioning, challenge incorrect premises, admit faults, and turn down unbefitting requests.",
    "In this regard, a GPT-3.5 series model that completed its training at the beginning of year 2022, was used in the interface construction.",
    "Microsoft Azure's AI supercomputing power was used in training ChatGPT and GPT-3.5."
  ]
}